  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-010">No new top-level Program.cs lines; resolver already registered in `AnalysisServicesModule`.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">Factory remains AI-internal; CRUD-side callers don't see the resolver.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-015">No user message content logged when persona resolution emits telemetry.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-029">Verify BFF publish-size delta; ≤+5 MB R6 budget per NFR-02.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-01">Conversational primacy — scopes augment but NEVER replace conversational ability. Even with a strict CUST- persona, the agent still responds conversationally to any turn.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-10">8K system prompt budget preserved. Resolved persona text must fit within the existing `PlaybookChatContextProvider` budget.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-13">Safety pipeline (PromptShield + Groundedness + Citations + Privilege + Cross-matter middleware chain) unchanged.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec FR-03">Resolution order = global SYS- → tenant CUST- → playbook-attached (most specific wins per Q1).</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec FR-04">With no override, system prompt MUST be byte-identical to pre-cutover output.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project CLAUDE.md MUST NOT">MUST NOT hardcode persona text in C# after this task lands (data-driven only).</constraint>
  </constraints>

