    <criterion testable="true">With no tenant/playbook override, assembled system prompt is byte-identical to pre-cutover output (FR-04 regression test passes).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">With CUST- override mocked, persona text used; conversational layer intact (NFR-01 test passes).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`BuildDefaultSystemPrompt()` either removed OR retained as null-safety assertion only (data-driven cutover binding per project CLAUDE.md MUST NOT).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">8K system prompt budget unchanged (NFR-10).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Safety pipeline middleware chain unchanged (NFR-13).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">No user message content logged in telemetry (ADR-015).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">BFF publish-size delta reported; ≤+5 MB R6 total budget verified.</criterion>
